{"tid":185280,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"廿幾年濕疹 好返8-9成 開心share","createTime":"2017-04-03T10:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T07:05:47.000Z","uid":86432,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3cb02dbc4f91becb737688c181809de47b83b155","tid":185280,"uid":86432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T10:59:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n我係一個長期濕疹人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3歲已經開始有濕疹 都廿幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n額頭 面 咀 關節位 手背 手掌 度度都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老老竇竇 真係好影響社交<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地一見到你隻手咁樣樣 嚇撚到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為啲仆街濕疹俾人飛  個人變到閃閃縮縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己本身好貪靚 越大啲濕疹越嚴重<br />\n搽類固醇搽到冇效 越發越多 越來越嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲搞到自己有抑鬱症狀 屌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好 入正題<br />\n最近有朋友介紹左一隻中藥藥膏 <br />\n搽左兩個禮拜左右<br />\n竟然好返8-9成<br />\n（其實我諗左好耐打唔打 因為好怕俾人話我打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  問候埋我家人）<br />\n<br />\n有圖有真相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係FB訂 一支都係40蚊 試下無妨<br />\n個page有好多患者好返既圖 （好多濕疹bb)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋個板主有拎支藥膏去做化驗<br />\n有貼埋化驗報告出黎 證明冇類固醇<br />\n而且重點係 板主超級有耐性 會打好多字教你點用 又有交帶<br />\n<br />\n（再利申一次 非打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  自己真金白銀買黎用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲都係受濕疹困擾 已經自暴自棄 <br />\n都不妨試下隻藥膏<br />\n<br />\n但係！我帶返個頭盔先<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">用之前請咨詢醫生意見 始終都係藥黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\nFB page:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望濕疹既各位早日康復 快高長大<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n得閒再分享下自己用咩skincare<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee351bcc0fa4833552f6bf80fa01bd659cde9834","tid":185280,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:02:11.000Z","msg":"又賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f463b3298773d444f25604f2f8a0b4f7fcf6929","tid":185280,"uid":86432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:11:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打 你有冇濕疹？<br />\n你明白有濕疹有幾辛苦嗎？<br />\n放上黎只係希望有濕疹既人可以快啲好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efcc2034c05c237c6a02aa1c77f18bf30fab3087","tid":185280,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:11:26.000Z","msg":"絲打係紅印類濕疹定發炎出水果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d0cdb7374bda459e6d72e36bdf98ef939f0a5b","tid":185280,"uid":86432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:15:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打係紅印類濕疹定發炎出水果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗我兩種都有<br />\n我最嚴重既時候 手背係一大忽紅印 一個個圈咁<br />\n手指係發炎腫起有水泡<br />\n你睇上面張圖都會見到我啲手甲床位係腫起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訓教會忍唔住R R到標晒黃色水 流晒血<br />\n啲皮又乾又厚 手指係屈唔到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1737e94a97ee725adcde18cd74e704c27a20da3c","tid":185280,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:33:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>絲打係紅印類濕疹定發炎出水果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗我兩種都有<br />\n我最嚴重既時候 手背係一大忽紅印 一個個圈咁<br />\n手指係發炎腫起有水泡<br />\n你睇上面張圖都會見到我啲手甲床位係腫起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訓教會忍唔住R R到標晒黃色水 流晒血<br />\n啲皮又乾又厚 手指係屈唔到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同我好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我最近好返到得返紅印無出水"},{"pid":"7474963a7510d955023f77ba9568b28d0b6b11d3","tid":185280,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:36:26.000Z","msg":"醫心先係上策，同D19親戚反哂面，即刻好返哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b8e0deff8668bdb54caba4a85fdfe9b213aaf6","tid":185280,"uid":86432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>絲打係紅印類濕疹定發炎出水果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗我兩種都有<br />\n我最嚴重既時候 手背係一大忽紅印 一個個圈咁<br />\n手指係發炎腫起有水泡<br />\n你睇上面張圖都會見到我啲手甲床位係腫起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訓教會忍唔住R R到標晒黃色水 流晒血<br />\n啲皮又乾又厚 手指係屈唔到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同我好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我最近好返到得返紅印無出水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我發現一食菇就會起水泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔敢再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b900ba4d5617463ed4528fdaf70fa5e329c29a59","tid":185280,"uid":98897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T12:03:22.000Z","msg":"哦 個枝大陸狼毒藥膏呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  人地大陸政府都驗得超哂標啦D抗生素激素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   自己衡量下用唔用啦  亦唔好亂介紹比人用啦  正如個枝皮炎平999 我都奶過野啦  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 包你幾年後包得仲勁  祝君好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有D人係想戒類固醇嫁 唔好害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係大陸激素=類固醇呀<br />\n    <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比埋條LINK你又點話: <a href=\"http://www.gansu.gov.cn/art/2015/6/21/art_36_241214.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gansu.gov.cn%2Fart%2F2015%2F6%2F21%2Fart_36_241214.html&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=e1a3445a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.gansu.gov.cn/art/2015/6/21/art_36_241214.html</a>"},{"pid":"bba966bf0fd0c6e30bffb61ab941f88d41ba6e4f","tid":185280,"uid":69320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:24:01.000Z","msg":"我都係一出世就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家大左其實好少會再起，除非轉天氣<br />\n反而最困擾既係d印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一撻二撻 夏天熱到pk都唔著得短褲短裙 <br />\n去遊水就更加唔洗講<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0295490bd2e1a325b5e67c0d3fc4a47342d743f7","tid":185280,"uid":15125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:29:16.000Z","msg":"一歲開始有咗十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最嚴重係小四成條頸流哂血 <br />\n晚晚用冷氣吹涷張被包住先瞓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依加食中藥加用死海鹽<br />\n真係好好多<br />\n特別係食中藥<br />\n一定要堅持<br />\n雖然真係好撚難飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係見到自己皮膚滑返真係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001a97961e0d59e7aaa46913597cbcaa70bc8854","tid":185280,"uid":67867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:33:01.000Z","msg":"絲打想同下有冇戒口<br />\n飲食我完全失控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bdae6650d2485fd61d808f5eb6a059f438d247a","tid":185280,"uid":67867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T14:33:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打想<span style=\"color: red;\">問下你</span>有冇戒口<br />\n飲食我完全失控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"45941560ccabf68fd9498edb04884f99d4ee563f","tid":185280,"uid":100545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T06:11:47.000Z","msg":"濕疹L 留名 其實做好保濕先係最重要<br />\n類固醇真係不治本"},{"pid":"9b4431f0459bf955f9a5daab4163940035f0a311","tid":185280,"uid":27256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:29:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>濕疹L 留名 其實做好保濕先係最重要<br />\n類固醇真係不治本</blockquote><br />\n要點保濕法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506af0ed19165e235f0e1214831bc7cc4f17c0d5","tid":185280,"uid":100545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T08:04:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>濕疹L 留名 其實做好保濕先係最重要<br />\n類固醇真係不治本</blockquote><br />\n要點保濕法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最近用緊CETAPHIL 醫學配方果隻沖涼同CREAM<br />\n不過都唔平一枝成3舊水 買SET 裝平少少都要5百幾"},{"pid":"a0733c38cf2a109c167d79bf90c434c06ae1d04a","tid":185280,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB